en_66309_0	India’s popular anti-corruption activist Annaa Hasaare is getting ready for a Sri Lankan tour.
en_66309_1	‘Times of India’ citing Annaa Hasaare’s lawyer said that most probably Annaa Hasaare’s Sri Lankan tour would take place this month.
en_66309_2	‘Times of India’ said that the tour was taking place in accordance with an invitation from several civil organizations in Sri Lanka.
en_66309_3	The newspaper said that in addition Annaa Hasaare would undertake a tour of Canada as well.
en_66309_4	Annaa Hasaare carried out a fast in 2011demanding that an anti-corruption bill be passed in the Indian parliament.
en_66309_5	As a result of this Annaa Hasaare is considered an anti-corruption activist in India
